ing pipeline. Automate WordPress post creation, SEO optimization, image formatting, and cross-platform distribution. Manage Ghost, Webflow, and CMS updates effortlessly.', '简化内容发布流程。自动化 WordPress 文章创建、SEO 优化、图片格式调整及跨平台分发。轻松管理 Ghost、Webflow 和各类 CMS 更新。', null, 'false', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/n8n_json_storage/zips/wordpress-cms-ops.zip'), ('575225c5-84a5-4ec3-b4cb-fd4be2823c80', '2025-12-26 04:13:57.401341+00', 'voice-audio-ai', 'Voice & Audio AI', '语音识别与合成', 'Leverage AI for audio processing. Workflows for transcribing meetings with Whisper, generating realistic speech (TTS), and summarizing podcasts. Integrate with OpenAI and specialized audio APIs.', '利用 AI 处理音频内容。包含使用 Whisper 转录会议记录、生成逼真语音 (TTS) 以及自动总结播客内容的模版。完美集成 OpenAI 及各类音频 API。', null, 'false', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/n8n_json_storage/zips/voice-audio-ai.zip'), ('5d00a9a3-5ec5-49de-aa51-0538837ae3ff', '2025-12-26 04:13:59.786508+00', 'youtube-video-ops', 'YouTube & Video Ops', '视频运营自动化', 'Automate your YouTube channel management. Auto-upload videos, sync metadata, track analytics, and repurpose video clips for TikTok/Shorts. Streamline your video production workflow.', '实现 YouTube 频道管理自动化。自动上传视频、同步元数据、追踪数据分析，并将长视频自动剪辑分发至 TikTok/Shorts。简化视频制作与运营流程。', null, 'false', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/n8n_json_storage/zips/youtube-video-ops.zip'), ('6333f5be-561d-4ae9-b433-2587187d50ec', '2025-12-26 04:14:01.662681+00', 'devops-monitoring', 'DevOps & Monitoring', '运维监控', 'Essential DevOps automations for developers. Monitor server uptime, automate CI/CD pipelines, manage Docker containers, and receive instant alerts for system outages via Webhooks.', '开发者必备的 DevOps 自动化工具。监控服务器在线状态、自动化 CI/CD 流程、管理 Docker 容器，并通过 Webhook 接收系统宕机即时报警。', null, 'false', 'https://storage.googleapis.com/n8n_json_storage/zips/devops-monitoring.zip'), ('6c2cbe55-c3d6-47be-a88a-65c9a743a7b4', '2025-12-26 04:14:00.979421+00', 'crm-sync-workflows', 'CRM Sync Workflows', 'CRM 客户数据同步', 'Keep your customer data consistent across pla